    </task>
    <!-- Consider removing the next task for the next edition; this makes more sense for proving that a bipartite graph has chromatic number 2. -->
    <task>
      <statement>
        <p>
          If you used the same procedure to color a cycle, will you always be able to color it with two colors?
        </p>
